Package: mulgar
Title: Functions for pre-processing data for multivariate data visualisation using tours
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Dianne",
           family = "Cook",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dicook@monash.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3813-7155")),
    person(given = "Ursula", 
           family = "Laa", 
           email = "ursula.laa@boku.ac.at", 
           role = "ctb", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0249-6439")))
Description: This is a companion to the book 
  [Interactive and dynamic graphics for high-dimensional data using R](https://dicook.github.io/mulgar_book/) 
  by Cook and Laa. It contains useful functions for processing data in preparation for 
  visualising with a tour. There are also several sample data sets.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    geozoo,
    tourr,
    tibble,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    purrr
Suggests:
    ggdendro,
    colorspace,
